Developer Terms of Use
des:
Track your water intake straight to your Fitbit dashboard.

Volumes supported at the moment:
Glass: 8.45 fl oz ("Alexa tell aqua log one glass of water")
Bottle: 16.9 fl oz ("Alexa tell aqua log one bottle of water")
Cup: 8.45 fl oz
Mug: 8.45 fl oz
Can: 11.16 fl oz
